parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as they are designed to provide crucial protection to occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy during a crash
despite meeting the deployment threshold; occupants may experience injuries or fatalities as a result.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The disintegration of the dashboard can cause small particles to blow into the driver's face, creating a distraction and potentially causing an accident.
symptoms: The dashboard is disintegrating
small particles are blowing into the driver's face
particularly when the heater or air conditioner is on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rusting of the frame can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to potential safety risks.
symptoms: Rusting of the frame behind the front wheels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the door lock mechanism can cause doors to become stuck or unable to open, potentially trapping occupants inside the vehicle.
symptoms: Doors fail to open from inside and outside
door locks jam intermittently
door handles cannot be opened from the outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and even rollovers, which can result in serious harm or fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes lock up
the vehicle spins or swerves out of control
the brake pedal becomes soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
extended stopping distance
brakes fade away.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Problems with the brake pedal can lead to extended stopping distances, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal becomes soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the brake pedal becomes very hard
extended stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unusual brake noise and corrosion can indicate worn or damaged brake components, which can lead to brake failure and accidents.
symptoms: The brakes make a noise
corroded brake rotors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Complete brake failure and linkage problems can cause accidents, injuries, and even fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes do not work at all
too much play in the linkages.
